===Etymology 1===
From French ''[[apostrophe#French|apostrophe]]'', or Latin ''[[apostrophus]]'', from Greek [[απόστροφος]] ‘accent of elision’, a noun use of an adjective from [[αποστρέφειν]] ‘turn away’.

